{"tid":534434,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[炎拳睇完大結局","createTime":"2018-01-19T18:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T00:51:07.000Z","uid":14100,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d62218719b55051b03d9e1b30edf00e7b5365d71","tid":534434,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"屌你做乜鳩？！故事暴走<br />\n阿格尼成日神志不清，之後失控<br />\n<br />\n桑無啦啦變咗大佬，比主角殺咗，主角就取代桑<br />\n所謂冰之魔女無啦啦岀場，之後無啦啦玩咩神樹，又突然變幹部又突然俾桑秒咗<br />\n<br />\n阿格尼明明冇咗火，又突然可以玩點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n桑枝木棍又會無啦啦生棵野岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結局又無啦啦幾千萬年後地球爆咗<br />\n<br />\n有冇神人可以解釋下？？"},{"pid":"59cc62720aeec835d0b5903b24fde446c6a6a7be","tid":534434,"uid":71322,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"呢套野去到冰之魔女出現個下 開始亂尻咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35fe5bb014d5bd2536edd306877be1f03edfe36","tid":534434,"uid":71322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T19:35:43.000Z","msg":"Btw 阿格尼可以點火係因為佢仍然係再生能力者 而普通火炎係可以整熄 所以點火就變炎拳 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15bb9f9fbe0495830213778e55ffb3231be0819","tid":534434,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 阿格尼可以點火係因為佢仍然係再生能力者 而普通火炎係可以整熄 所以點火就變炎拳 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但講到(復原後)佢仲可以無啦啦爆火，d人熄唔到咁<br />\n<br />\n桑又突然勁咗咁多<br />\n(偽)冰之魔女以為幾勁點知俾桑秒"},{"pid":"0316117193aa4710043ec8f9f95f649370054818","tid":534434,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套野去到冰之魔女出現個下 開始亂尻咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n打三個死刑犯時都仲ok"},{"pid":"187ccc2a765686efe2dafe43ac9a366e83b4a011","t